              <strong>⚠️ Important:</strong> Please read these Terms carefully before using our services. These Terms constitute a legally binding agreement between you and CyberBros Security.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Definitions -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">2. Definitions</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li><strong class="text-white">"Services"</strong> refers to cybersecurity training, awareness programs, consultations, and educational services provided by CyberBros Security.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white">"Website"</strong> refers to cyberbrosecurity.work and all related subdomains.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white">"User", "You", "Your"</strong> refers to any individual or entity accessing our website or using our services.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white">"Content"</strong> refers to text, images, videos, code, and other materials available on our website.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white">"Client"</strong> refers to institutions, organizations, or individuals who engage our paid services.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Use of Services -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">3. Use of Services</h2>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-indigo-400 mb-3 mt-6">3.1 Eligibility</h3>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">
            You must be at least 18 years old to use our services. By using our services, you represent and warrant that you meet this age requirement and have the legal capacity to enter into these Terms.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-indigo-400 mb-3 mt-6">3.2 Account Registration</h3>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">
            Some services may require you to create an account or provide personal information. You agree to:
