            Our total liability shall not exceed the amount paid by you for services in the 12 months preceding the claim.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Indemnification -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">8. Indemnification</h2>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">
            You agree to indemnify, defend, and hold harmless CyberBros Security, its officers, employees, and affiliates from any claims, damages, losses, liabilities, and expenses (including legal fees) arising from:
